<Layout title="AI-Enhanced Operations | Intelio - Scale Without Multiplying Headcount" description="Scale your operations without headcount multiplication. AI extracts data, scores leads, detects patterns. Humans make decisions. Same team handles 2-3x volume.">
<main class="bg-white">
  <!-- HERO SECTION: Video Background -->
  <section class="relative h-[600px] md:h-[450px] sm:h-[300px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-black">
    <!-- Video Background -->
    <video 
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      preload="auto"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
    >
      <source src="/videos/system-integration-hero.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>
    
    <!-- Dark Overlay for Text Readability -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/45 z-[1]"></div>

    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-[48px] md:text-[36px] sm:text-[24px] text-white mb-4 leading-[1.2] font-normal tracking-[-0.5px]">
        Scale Operations Without Multiplying Headcount
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-base sm:text-sm text-[#f0f0f0] leading-relaxed font-normal max-w-[600px] mx-auto">
        AI extracts data from documents. Scores leads consistently. Detects risk patterns. Your team handles 2-3x volume with the same people.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-[900px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-6 sm:px-6">
    <!-- THE PROBLEM SECTION -->
    <section class="pt-24 md:pt-16 sm:pt-12 pb-12 border-b border-gray-200">
      <h2 class="text-[32px] md:text-[24px] sm:text-[24px] text-black mb-4 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
        What's Broken Today
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-black leading-relaxed mb-12 font-normal">
        Volume grows. Your team doesn't. Manual work doesn't scale without hiring people. And decisions lack consistency because they rely on individual judgment.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Manual Data Extraction
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            Invoices, contracts, applications arrive as PDFs. Someone manually reads them, extracts structured data, enters it into systems. Slow, error-prone, and doesn't scale.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Inconsistent Decision-Making
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            Leads scored by intuition. Accuracy depends on who does it. Approvals decided by gut feel. Same requests get different outcomes. Patterns invisible because decisions aren't systematic.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            No Early Warning System
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            Problems emerge late. Customer churn discovered after they're gone. Project timeline slips at deadline. Market shifts discovered after you've lost ground. No systematic pattern detection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Scaling Requires Headcount
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            As volume grows, you hire more people to handle same tasks. Document processing needs another person. Lead scoring needs another person. No leverage, just multiplication.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHAT CHANGES SECTION -->
    <section class="pt-12 pb-12 border-b border-gray-200">
      <h2 class="text-[32px] md:text-[24px] sm:text-[24px] text-black mb-4 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
        What Changes After Deployment
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-black leading-relaxed mb-12 font-normal">
        AI handles pattern-matching and information assembly. Your team handles judgment. Same headcount, 2-3x volume, better decisions.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Automatic Data Extraction
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            Documents arrive, structured data extracted automatically, validated for accuracy, ready for use. Manual data entry eliminated. Accuracy improves over time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Systematic Decision-Making
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            AI applies same logic consistently. Lead scoring uses explicit criteria, not gut. Approvals evaluated against historical data. Decisions are repeatable and measurable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Proactive Pattern Detection
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            System continuously monitors operations and surfaces patterns you wouldn't see manually. Churn risk detected early. Timeline slips detected before crisis. Market shifts visible in data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Context-Rich Decisions
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            When someone needs to decide, all relevant context is automatically assembled. "Is this customer profitable?" answered with complete financial context in seconds.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-8 md:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="text-xl text-black mb-3 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
            Headcount-Independent Scaling
          </h3>
          <p class="text-base text-black leading-relaxed font-normal">
            Same number of people handle 2-3x volume. AI handles the pattern-matching and information assembly. People handle the judgment. Volume growth doesn't require proportional hiring.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS SECTION -->
    <section class="pt-12 pb-12 border-b border-gray-200">
      <h2 class="text-[32px] md:text-[24px] sm:text-[24px] text-black mb-4 font-normal leading-[1.4]">
        How the System Actually Works
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-black mb-12 leading-relaxed font-normal">
        AI understands data, identifies patterns, scores and classifies, then presents recommendations. Humans stay in control of all decisions.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
